      <scopecontent id="aspace_24c2fd4dd44a0fdf892b9b7890903c95">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The papers consist of correspondence between Thomas R. Hill, Jennie M. Hill, Angelo Heilprin, and others, Thomas Hill's journal and drawings of gold mining in Alaska, and papers of the Philadelphia Exploration and Mining Company, which organized to mine in Alaska.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
